<div class="content" name="GetQueueList_Line" uuid="02a71aa0-cd50-406b-a0c5-41b2f2cf78bc"><p>The GetQueueList packet is transmitted from a TAPI <a href="489de77f-16d8-4c4f-939a-f795e8b42893#gt_60e0e1fa-66fe-41e1-b5e3-ceab97e53506" data-linktype="relative-path">client</a> to a TAPI <a href="489de77f-16d8-4c4f-939a-f795e8b42893#gt_434b0234-e970-4e8c-bdfa-e16a30d96703" data-linktype="relative-path">server</a> in a <a href="489de77f-16d8-4c4f-939a-f795e8b42893#gt_8a7f6700-8311-45bc-af10-82e10accd331" data-linktype="relative-path">remote procedure call</a>.
Sending this packet returns a list of queues that are associated with a
particular ACD group. It generates a <a href="5221aa4e-0034-4756-bbc7-35c6c14b69a2" data-linktype="relative-path">LINE_PROXYREQUEST</a> packet
to be sent to a <a href="489de77f-16d8-4c4f-939a-f795e8b42893#gt_624ba2cf-5c41-45cd-9334-84fbc089d34f" data-linktype="relative-path">registered
proxy function handler</a>, referencing a <a href="68c27048-6ad3-4c35-aeab-8e1d260923f0" data-linktype="relative-path">LINEPROXYREQUEST</a> packet of
type LINEPROXYREQUEST_GETQUEUELIST.</p><table>
